#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the user manual for &kphotoalbum; &mdash; a digital image "
"cataloguing software that supports annotation, browsing, searching and "
"viewing of digital images and videos. If you are not the type who likes "
"reading documentation, but rather just want to try out things, here are a "
"few alternatives:"
msgstr ""
"To je uporabniški priročnik za &kphotoalbum; &mdash; programska oprema za "
"katalogizacijo digitalnih slik, ki podpira opombe, brskanje, iskanje in "
"ogled digitalnih slik in videoposnetkov. Če niste tip, ki rad bere "
"dokumentacijo, ampak želite stvari samo preizkusiti, je tukaj nekaj možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; Homepage</"
"ulink>, and look at the quick overview, screen shoots, and introduction "
"videos."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na <ulink url=\"http://www.kphotoalbum.org/\">&kphotoalbum; Domača "
"stran</ulink> in si oglejte hiter pregled, posnetke zaslona in "
"predstavitvene videe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &kphotoalbum;, and accept its offer for a demo (If this is your first "
"time you start it), or go to <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu and select "
"<guimenuitem>Run &kphotoalbum; demo</guimenuitem>. That will load "
"&kphotoalbum; with a number of images, and let you browse around."
msgstr ""
"Zaženite &kphotoalbum; in sprejmite njegovo ponudbo za predstavitev (če ga "
"zaženete prvič) ali pojdite v meni <guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu> in izberite "
"<guimenuitem>Zaženi &kphotoalbum; demo</guimenuitem>. To bo naložilo "
"&kphotoalbum; s številnimi slikami in vam omogoča brskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you prefer to print out this document, then you may find it as on long "
"PDF document at <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; docs</ulink>. A "
"direct link is available at <ulink url=\"http://kphotoalbum.org/index.php?"
"page=documentation\">&kphotoalbum;'s Homepage</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ta dokument raje natisniti, ga boste morda našli kot dolg dokument "
"PDF na <ulink url=\"http://docs.kde.org/\">&kde; dokumenti</ulink>. "
"Neposredna povezava je na voljo na <ulink url=\"http://kphotoalbum.org/index."
"php?page=documentation\">domači strani &kphotoalbum;</ulink>."

